GLOBAL UI FRAMEWORK (ALL ROLES)
Shell (Persistent)
┌───────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Top Bar: Org Name | Role | Alerts | Profile   │
├──────────────┬────────────────────────────────┤
│ Left Nav     │ Main Content Area               │
│ (Role-Based) │ (Evidence-Driven Views)         │
└──────────────┴────────────────────────────────┘

Universal UI Rules

No edit icons on historical records

Status badges are immutable

Evidence links always visible

Every screen shows “Last Evaluated At”

AI outputs are clearly labeled Advisory

